Movie: Landscape with the Fall of Icarus

Review: i’d say probably the most playlike film i’ve seen personally. very restrained. even a rather sparing use of closeups- most of them trained on brian cox’s steven. i think that endeared him to me. i like having a gander at people’s faces.
that shot of the yellow spider crawling between a guy’s fingers while another guy plays his little recorder i mean that’s what it’s all about that’s all there is
